folder: Victory Boulevard & Forest Avenue, Staten Island, NY
text:
Victory Boulevard, from Forest Avenue (left) to Woodstock Street, showing on the west side of the Boulevard, in the center of the view, the Jewish Community Center. The view is northwestern across Hero Park, toward the Upper Bay.
